  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 180°C. Grease a 20cm square baking dish with butter.",
    "Mix mirin-hon, flour, salt, and black pepper in a bowl.",
    "Press the mixture into the prepared baking dish.",
    "Dot the top with butter.",
    "Sprinkle breadcrumbs over the butter.",
    "Bake for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and let it cool for 5 minutes.",
    "Serve warm.",
    "Enjoy!"
